# Cloudflare Pages — redirect rules.
# Reference: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
# Format: <source> <destination> <status>   ( "!" makes it force-apply over a real file )

# Canonicalise www → apex so search engines don't split link equity between
# https://mohanan.uk/ and https://www.mohanan.uk/. The apex is the canonical
# everywhere on the portfolio (nav, OG metadata, JSON-LD, share links).
https://www.mohanan.uk/*  https://mohanan.uk/:splat  301!
